Class DoubleSupplierSpliterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.pr0methean.betterrandom.util.spliterator.AbstractSupplierSpliterator<DoubleSupplier,DoubleConsumer,DoubleSupplierSpliterator>
      • io.github.pr0methean.betterrandom.util.spliterator.DoubleSupplierSpliterator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Spliterator<Double>, Spliterator.OfDouble, Spliterator.OfPrimitive<Double,DoubleConsumer,Spliterator.OfDouble>

    public class DoubleSupplierSpliterator
extends AbstractSupplierSpliterator<DoubleSupplier,DoubleConsumer,DoubleSupplierSpliterator>
implements Spliterator.OfDouble
    An unordered, concurrent Spliterator.OfDouble that invokes a DoubleSupplier to get its values and has a preset size.
    Author:
    Chris Hennick
